This module contains routines for conversion between unicode
and Myanmar legacy encodings, such as zawgyi, wininwa.

This is a python port of Thanlwinsoft's javascript converter.

This module also comes with a script, namely myanmar-converter,
which can be used to convert encodings from CLI.


INSTALL
-------

Note: You must have python-chardet installed on your system.

To install, run this command.

    `python setup.py install`
